title: Amana Brand Gas and Electric Ranges
description: Amana brand cooktops provide precise temperature control with versatile burners, so you can simmer and boil just how you like. When you’re ready to heat up your oven, use our preset Bake Assist Temps for a quick and simple preheat. Just pick the temperature you want … press start … and you’re set to get cookin’. And thanks to generous oven capacity, you’ll never have to choose between dinner and dessert ... there’s plenty of room for multiple dishes. Finally, when it comes to cleanup, Self Clean Option lets the oven do the dirty work for you, so you can get back to relaxing.
